{
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.ancient": "Well, well, well, ain't you a new face?",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.next": "Greet",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/darv/darv_introduction",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.char": "I'm only passing through, I'm afraid.",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.next": "Continue",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.ancient": "Yeah. Sure. Wouldn't that be somethin'.",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/darv/darv_endeared",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0r.ancient": "Passin' through again, huh? Take one of these. On me.",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0r.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/darv/darv_endeared",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.ancient": "Hey, good on you for sticking it out, though.\nWoulda been easy to give up by now.",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.next": "Reply",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/darv/darv_endeared",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.char": "What choice do I have?",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.next": "Continue",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.ancient": "Could always walk away.\nIt'd piss off Neow, but...",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.next": "Disagree",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/darv/darv_fear",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-3.char": "Not while this world still suffers.",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.ancient": "[sine]..curious...\n...a new.. ..visitor...?[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.next": "Introduce yourself",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/neow/neow_curious",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.char": "I've come to find the master of this place.\nAnd make him stop this madness.",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.next": "Continue",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.ancient":"[sine]..Good... ..I... look.. ..forward...\n...to working... ...with you...[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/neow/neow_sleepy",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0r.ancient": "[sine]...no... peace.. ..while [red]he[/red] yet lives...[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0r.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/neow/neow_welcome",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.char": "Back again, once more...\nI suppose our arrangement continues.",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.next": "Continue",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.ancient": "[sine]...you.. will.. ..keep fighting...\n...until... ...it is done...[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/neow/neow_sleepy",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.ancient": "Who goes there? I don’t recall sending for an escort.",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.next": "Step forward",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/nonupeipe/nonupeipe_eeked",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.char": "Your guards let me in. It took only a few words.",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.next": "Continue",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.ancient": "They must have been convincing words indeed.\nCome in then, corvid. You’ve piqued my interest.",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/nonupeipe/nonupeipe_welcome",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0r.ancient": "Knives, and magic, and blades enchanted for war...\nThey all have their place. But you and I know our greatest weapon is charm.",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0r.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/nonupeipe/nonupeipe_welcome",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.ancient": "For a common raven, you carry yourself with grace.",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.next": "Bristle",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/nonupeipe/nonupeipe_giggle",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.char": "I will assume that is a compliment.",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.next": "Continue",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.ancient": "From me, pretty bird? It is.",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/nonupeipe/nonupeipe_giggle",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-0.ancient": "You’re certain I can’t convince you to serve a new mistress?\nNeow wastes your talents, crashing you against a wall and hoping that it breaks.",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-0.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/nonupeipe/nonupeipe_giggle",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-0.next": "Rebuff",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-1.char": "Your gifts are appreciated. But I need her power if I’m to claim the future I fight for.",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-1.next": "Continue",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-2.ancient": "What a shame. But the offer stands, if you ever change your mind.",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-2.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/nonupeipe/nonupeipe_grossed_out",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.ancient": "Bird!! Puppet bird! Why puppet? Why bird!?",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.next": "Answer",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.char": "I was simply born this way.",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.next": "Continue",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.char": "...And I am my own woman.\nNo matter what anyone has to say about it.",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.next": "Continue",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-3.ancient": "Wow!! Very good words! You lie and I believe!!",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0r.ancient": "Not-puppet puppet!! Got you shiny! Birds like shiny!",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.ancient": "Bird puppet! Don’t fight Architect! No good fight!",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.next": "Explain",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.char": "A mad king threatens what the people have built.\nHow could I stand by and do nothing?",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.next": "Continue",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.ancient": "Threaten bad! Fight worse! Cycle of violence!!",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.next": "Continue",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-3.char": "You can’t escape the cycle by letting the boot stomp on your face.",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.char": "At the risk of seeming glib... you're melting.",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.next": "Continue",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.ancient": "[thinky_dots]I am. Does it bother you...?[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.next": "Deny",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.char": "I worry that it bothers [b]you[/b].\nAnd even more that it does not.",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.next": "Continue",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-3.ancient": "[thinky_dots]Why would it?\nI sleep, and I am content...[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0r.ancient": "[thinky_dots]You won't accept things as they are.\nI will still offer what comfort I can...[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.ancient": "[thinky_dots]Why do you struggle so vainly...?[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.next": "Tell him",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.char": "If I believe I can change nothing, it will be true.",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.next": "Continue",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.ancient": "[thinky_dots]So small, and so desperate to matter.\nTake what you will, and leave me to my rest...[/thinky_dots]",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.ancient": "DAGGERS! AGAIN!! MY DISAPPOINTMENT IS INFINITE!!!",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.next": "Console",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/tanx/tanx_roar",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.char": "When my strength is not sufficient, I call upon the might of sorcery.",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.next": "Continue",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.ancient": "MAGIC IS MIGHT?? SHOW ME!!!",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/tanx/tanx_curiosity",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0r.ancient": "WEAPONS! TAKE A WEAPON! DO SWORD MAGIC NEXT TIME!!!",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0r.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/tanx/tanx_roar",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.ancient": "FIGHT ME, SORCERESS!!",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.next": "Fight",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/tanx/tanx_roar",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.char": "...!",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.next": "Play dead",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.ancient": "DEAD ALREADY! I THOUGHT YOU WERE STRONGER!",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.next": "Lie",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/tanx/tanx_roar",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-3.char": "It is true. I have no hope of victory without the aid of a mighty warrior.",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-3.next": "Continue",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-4.ancient": "YOU'RE RIGHT! TAKE THIS!!!",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-4.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/tanx/tanx_laugh",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.char": "It is nice to find somewhere warm, at least.",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.next": "Continue",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.ancient": "Oh, I can only [jitter][b]imagine[/b][/jitter].",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.next": "Startle",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.char": "Ah. My apologies. I didn't mean to intrude.",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.next": "Continue",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-3.ancient": "Not at all, not at all! Come in and make yourself at home.\nI'm always happy to welcome a [jitter][b]kindred spirit[/b][/jitter].",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0r.ancient": "I've seen so many fascinating flames lately, but only one quite like [jitter][b]yours[/b][/jitter].",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.ancient": "The others won't say it, but thank you for your restraint, dearie.",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.next": "Inquire",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.char": "What do you mean?",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.next": "Continue",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.ancient": "If you had your way, you'd cut us all down where we stand!\nJust because you [jitter][b]can't[/b][/jitter] doesn't mean I don't appreciate you haven't tried.",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-0.ancient": "You know, a mother's greatest joy is watching her little ones grow.",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-0.next": "Take the bait",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-1.char": "I have concerns about how you see our relationship.",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-1.next": "Continue",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-2.ancient": "[i][font_size=22]Tezcatara's laugh rumbles like a furnace.[/font_size][/i]",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-2.next": "Continue",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-3.ancient": "Oh, dearie, I didn't mean [jitter][b]that[/b][/jitter].\nYou'll understand someday. What you've [sine]missed[/sine].",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.char": "Architect! This madness has to end!",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.next": "Continue",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.ancient": "I agree.",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.next": "Doubt",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.char": "Somehow, I don't think you do.",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-attack": "Both",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0.ancient": "It seems I am plagued by bothersome crows. How unfortunate for me that I have to kill you again.",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0.next": "Defy",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-1.char": "Death does not scare me. And neither do you.",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-1.next": "Continue",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-2.char": "I won't falter in the face of evil.",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-2.next": "Fight",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-3.ancient": "Try it, bird.",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-attack": "Both",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0r.char": "Strike me down again! You will not stay my hand!",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0r.next": "Continue",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1r.ancient": "Pity.",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-attack": "Both",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-0r.ancient": "Why do you insist on this fruitless battle?",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-0r.next" : "Answer",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-1r.char": "Because this world can be better. And I would fall a thousand times if even just once will make it that way.",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-1r.next": "Continue",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-2r.ancient": "It won't.",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-attack": "Both",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.4-0r.char": "I will tear down everything you've built with my own bloody talons, if that's what it takes.",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.4-0r.next": "Continue",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.4-1r.ancient": "They can get bloodier.",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.4-attack": "Both",
  "VAKUU.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.ancient": "Look at you, hotshot. Why don't you sign right here and we'll get you some real [sine]power[/sine]?",
  "VAKUU.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.next": "Refuse",
  "VAKUU.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.char": "Do I look like a fool to you?",
  "VAKUU.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.next": "Continue",
  "VAKUU.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.ancient": "What, you want me to give you the hard sell? Fine! First one's [jitter][b]free[/b][/jitter].",
  "VAKUU.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0r.ancient": "Well if it isn't my favorite firebrand!\nThat was sarcasm. Take your pick and go.",
  "VAKUU.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.ancient": "It's a shame you won't work with me. You'd make a great [sine]tyrant[/sine].",
  "VAKUU.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.next": "Scoff",
  "VAKUU.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.char": "No gods and no masters.\nFor all people, not just me.",
  "VAKUU.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.next": "Continue",
  "VAKUU.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.ancient": "Yeah, you're a real bird of the people. But I've seen that flame of yours before.",
  "VAKUU.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.next": "Continue",
  "VAKUU.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-3.ancient": "The little voice that crackles in the embers of your soul... it ain't singing of [sine]liberation[/sine]."
}